                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>ὁ δᾶμος τῶν <name>Ἐγεσταίων</name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested"><name>Φάωνα</name> <persName type="attested"><name>Νύμφωνος</name></persName> <name>Σωπολιανόν</name></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/>ἀρετᾶς ἕνεκα 
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app><note>Text of I.Segesta</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>The people of the Segestans (dedicate this statue of) Phaon Sopolianos, son of Nymphon, on account of his excellence</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" source="http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR">
                <p>Il popolo dei Segestani (ha onorato/ha eretto la statua di) Phaon, figlio di Nymphon, Sopolianos, per il suo valore[transl. from I.Segesta]</p>
            </div>
